#offset WildernessSpecial

0
{
  name { A Busy Street  }
  desc {
"   You are standing on a busy street where scrawny, ragged stray 
cats are following anyone with a possible meal. All around you people
are meandering about trying to ready themselves for a day of fishing or
a long voyage at sea. To the east, a sign in the shape of a fish 
reads Aesiuppes Bait Shop hangs above a door. 
  }
  sector { City }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { n, Wilderness7:280 }
	to { s, 2 }
	to { 10, 1 }
	  keywords { shop }
  }
}

1
{
  name { Aesiuppe's Bait Shop  }
  desc {
"   You have entered the Aesiuppes Bait Shop. The building is small 
but the shop has all the necessary equipment for off-shore fishing
or to simply fish from the beach. In front of you is the help counter 
where the shopkeeper provides you with assistantce on a purchase or
just advice on what fishes are biting on today. On the wall behind
the counter are rods, hooks, lines, and all sorts of fishing lures.
  }
  flags { indoors, peaceful, no_magic }
  exits {
	to { 10, 0 }
	  keywords { pier }
  }
}

2
{
  name { The Pier  }
  desc {
"   You are standing at the beginning of a pier, where the weathered
planks lead you away from the shore. The sounds of waves crashing 
on the beach fill the air as every wave releases a moisture that
cools off the hot sunrays. There are sailors and fisherman all about
this part of the peir, loading and unloading their vessels.
  }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { n, 0 }
	to { s, 3 }
  }
}

3
{
  name { The Pier  }
  desc {
"   You are standing on the edge of the pier. The crowds subside at 
this end since most business is handled at the beginning of the pier.
One can hear the bargaining of patrons attempting to purchase a
ticket to leave the Wilderness region. The bantering of sailors
about to set sail is vaguely heard over the waves crashing into the pier 
  }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { n, 2 }
  }
}

10
{
  name { A Steep Volcano Slope  }
  desc {
"   You can barely make out the trail as you slowly continue up 
toward the crater. As you struggle up the steep slope the poisonus
fumes begin to smother the air, making breathing a challenge. Further
across the flank a lahar of mud burns its way down leaving
a smokey trail.
  }
  sector { Mountains }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { u, 11 }
	to { d, Wilderness1:587 }
  }
}

11
{
  name { A Steep Volcano Slope  }
  desc {
"   The stench increases becoming unbearable as you near the mouth
of the crater. This dangerous path is a gauntlet  of jagged
edged rocks, any slip can cause you great harm. One must be mindful
of the perils as this will be your last chance to turn back. The
petrified pumice is more evident as a slight tremor rearranges the
ground.
  }
  sector { Mountains }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { u, 12 }
	to { d, 10 }
  }
}

12
{
  name { The Edge of the Crater  }
  desc {
"   The pungent stench of sulphur singes the air as well as your lungs.
You notice that someone has been here since at the mouth you vaguely
see what seems to be a cairn. Giant gas fumacoles explode further 
along the mount sending rocks flying in all directions that loosens 
scree causing it to tumble down the mountain.
  }
  sector { Fire }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { n, 13 }
	to { d, 11 }
  }
}

13
{
  name { The Center of the Crater  }
  desc {
"   It's Hot!! Yellow deposits spew the putrid odor of sulphur.
A lake of burning lava burns before you with geisers bursting all
about you. Fiery tears rain from the sky, burning and dissolving
your skin. The incinerating heat blurrs your vision and the exploding
bubbles strike you blind, making it difficult to make you way.
  }
  sector { Fire }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { n, 14 }
	to { s, 12 }
	to { northeast, 15 }
	to { northwest, 16 }
  }
}

14
{
  name { The Center of the Crater  }
  desc {
"   You stand in the middle of a seething sea of molten lava. 
Bubbling and grumbling with a tiny display of its pyrotechnics,
the volcano reminds you of it's devastating fury. Geysers are
bursting more rapidly, the droplets penetrate your
armor burning your skin.
  }
  sector { Fire }
  flags { no_sum }
  exits {
	to { e, 15 }
	to { s, 13 }
	to { w, 16 }
  }
}

